The gap from VS2 to VVS at 6ct costs $75,000–$90,000. That premium covers inclusions visible only under 10× magnification. At 11.7mm face-up diameter in a round brilliant cut, VS2 inclusions do not appear to the naked eye. The VVS tier at 6ct is a pure certificate-grade purchase — there is no visual benefit in normal wear.

